This is libplusplus, an extremely easy to use C++ library which is designed to
simply your programming tasks. Currently, it offers the following features:

- Portablility: tested on FreeBSD 4.8, 5.0 and 5.1, Linux 2.2.20, 2.4.20,
                2.4.21.
- Networking: Includes support for client/server applications using IPv4
              networks. IPX is supported, but currently FreeBSD only
- Configuration files: Can parse Samba-style configuration files.
- Databases: Portable database API, currently only MySQL supported
- Examples: A load of neat examples can be found in the examples/ directory.

Should any bugs or problems be encountered, feel free to contact me at
rink+libplusplus at il dot fontys dot nl
